casebody.data:
Second Department,

November, 1981

(November 2, 1981) Rose Ambrosio, Appellant, v John H. Fisher, Respondent.

Appeal from an order of the Supreme Court, Suffolk County (Mclnerney, J.), dated October 14, 1980, dismissed, without costs or disbursements. The order is reviewed upon the appeal from a judgment of the same court, entered October 21, 1980 (see Matter of Aho, 39 NY2d 241, 248). Judgment entered October 21, 1980 affirmed, without costs or disbursements. No opinion. Hopkins, J. P., Damiani, Titone and Mangano, JJ., concur.
